{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/140/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"ToyCon's Blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"31a512a3-96fb-50b8-b6fa-8842e8ad4e11","excerpt":"문자 반복 출력하기 https://school.programmers.co.kr/learn/courses/30/lessons/120825 변수 문자열 my_string 정수 n 제한사항 2 ≤ my_string 길이 ≤ 5 2 ≤ n ≤ 10 \"my_string…","html":"<h3>문자 반복 출력하기</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://school.programmers.co.kr/learn/courses/30/lessons/120825\">https://school.programmers.co.kr/learn/courses/30/lessons/120825</a></p>\n<h4>변수</h4>\n<p>문자열 my_string<br>\n정수 n</p>\n<h4>제한사항</h4>\n<p>2 ≤ my_string 길이 ≤ 5<br>\n2 ≤ n ≤ 10<br>\n\"my_string\"은 영어 대소문자</p>\n<h4>풀이</h4>\n<p>문자열을 그대로 반복하는게 아니라 글자별로 반복하는 구조다. 배열로 분해한 다음 각 원소를 n번씩 반복해서 합치는 방식으로 풀었다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>my_string을 배열로 변환</li>\n<li>map 메서드 실행, 콜백 함수로 e => e = e.repeat(n) 실행</li>\n<li>join('') 메서드 실행</li>\n<li>my_string 반환</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>코드</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">solution</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">my_string<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> n</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>my_string<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">map</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> e <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">join</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"문자 반복 출력하기","date":"April 05, 2023","description":"https://school.programmers.co.kr/learn/courses/30/lessons/120825"}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/139/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"문자열 뒤집기"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/141/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"특정 문자 제거하기"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"31a512a3-96fb-50b8-b6fa-8842e8ad4e11","previousPostId":"f8701b4d-3898-5b2b-9548-fb75f687fa34","nextPostId":"24f6c011-e1f7-560c-b90b-0d17b876b8db"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3257411868"],"slicesMap":{}}